articles.title: Whooping cough: Nine infant deaths reported as cases keep rising - BBC.com
articles.description: Experts worry this is a peak year for whooping cough, which is particularly dangerous for babies.
articles.content:
Nine babies have died from whooping cough since November 2023, with cases continuing to rise, the UK Health Security Agency says.
